UID:-Zv1YBuvwrMdVaIPJD75c
SUMMARY:Clock-Out Lounge Presents: Grrrl Gang w/ hi hi hi guests tba
DTSTAMP:20260314T160737Z
DTSTART:20260328T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Clock-Out Lounge Presents:Grrrl Gangw/ hi hi hiplus guests tba 
	Saturday March 28th8:30 doors 21+ $20adv/$25 dos https://grrrlgang.bandcam
	p.com/musicGrrrl Gang is not your typical indie pop band. Hailing from Yog
	yakarta\\\, Indonesia\\\, a city known for its rich cultural heritage and 
	artistic spirit\\\, Grrrl Gang combines punk attitude with pop sensibility
